  <sect2 role="package">
    <title>Introduction to Atkmm</title>

    <para>
      <application>Atkmm</application> is the official C++ interface for the
      ATK accessibility toolkit library.
    </para>

    &lfs10_checked;

    <bridgehead renderas="sect3">Package Information</bridgehead>
